ways to give colours--
----3 ways-----
1. hexadecimal
2.rgb
3. rgba 

HEXADECIMAL ---> start with # . jis colour ko jyada amount m denge uss colour(RGB) ki trf tend krega hmara colour.
                2 digit se particular color represent kiya jaata h . if we add two more digit in the last then it will represent the alpha channel , iski range vhi 00 se ff tk.
RGB -----> 0-255 tk ki range hoti h.
RGBa----> a stands for alpha channel that tells us about the opacity . range from 0-1.
alpha ki value jitni kam utni opacity jyada hoti h.
alpha ki value jyada , hmara colour utna hi jyada dikhegi.
